  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-03 stale input data)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 2. Full 13-factor assessment: 7 factors assessed (all meeting required levels), 6 factors not assessed (acceptable at MRL 2). NOTE: boundary-condition dataset was locked in Q4 2025; a minor model revision was issued in Q1 2026 to update turbulence-model constants. Re-validation against the revised boundary conditions is planned but not yet completed.",
