    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at level 1 per ASME V&V 40-2018 guidance for MRL 2 devices. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the COU decision that CFD can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The boundary-condition dataset predates the January 2026 model revision; re-validation is planned for Q2 2026 and does not preclude acceptance at this stage.",
